('PA166184404','Swissmedic',0,'The Swiss drug label for tamsulosin (Pradif) and tamsulosin and dutasteride (Duodart) states that since CYP3A4 inhibitors can significantly influence exposure to tamsulosin in CYP2D6 poor metabolizers, all tamsulosin treated patients should avoid strong CYP3A4 inhibitors.'),
